 Bottleshop E-commerce App

Welcome to the mozzify E-commerce application, built with Django. This application allows users to browse, search, and purchase bottles of beverages, including wines, spirits, and other drinks.

Features

- **User Authentication**: Users can register, log in, and manage their profiles.
- **Product Listings**: Display a variety of beverages with detailed product descriptions.
- **Search Functionality**: Users can search for specific products by name, category, or brand.
- **Shopping Cart**: Add items to the shopping cart and update quantities.
- **Checkout**: Secure checkout process using payment gateways (Stripe, PayPal, etc.).
- **Order History**: Users can view their previous orders and order status.
- **Admin Panel**: Manage products, categories, and orders through Django's admin panel.


Project Structure

```
mozzea/
│
├── manage.py              # Django project management script
├── requirements.txt       # Project dependencies
├── README.md              # Project documentation
│
├── mozzea/            # Project settings and configurations
│   ├── settings.py
│   ├── urls.py
│   ├── wsgi.py
│   └── ...
│
├── products/              # Products app (for managing products and categories)
│   ├── models.py
│   ├── views.py
│   ├── templates/
│   └── ...
│
├── cart/                  # Cart app (for managing shopping cart)
│   ├── models.py
│   ├── views.py
│   ├── templates/
│   └── ...
│
├── orders/                # Orders app (for managing orders and checkout)
│   ├── models.py
│   ├── views.py
│   ├── templates/
│   └── ...
└── ...
```

